Overview
===========================

The dns service listen for attach/detach floating ip to an instance and 
update dns server accordingly.


Configuration
===========================

TODO

The server saves logs to ``/var/log/nova/nova-dns.log``.


RPM Building
===========================

Clone nova-dns git repository, rename the top dir to nova-dns-VERSION,
and tar it to nova-dns-VERSION.tar.gz. Place it to rpmbuild/SOURCES
directory and run::

    $ rpmbuild -ba nova-dns.spec


Quickstart
===========================

Install the package::

    # yum install nova-dns

Start the server::

    # /etc/init.d/nova-dns start

Now instance state changes will be stored to a database.

